    name: 'Azuki x SATOSHI NAKAMOTO',
    'content': `<p>Get an inside look behind the unique fashion collaboration, featuring Azuki co-founder Zagabond.</p><img src="https://www.azuki.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fj7912igus1qi%2F7j1OOAt2fK1ywid2T7wS1F%2Ff5e21836f557b46a060d6cd8058da0e8%2F1582.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" alt="1582.png"><img src="https://www.azuki.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fj7912igus1qi%2F4xnvvQe3UnitPI8cOi9ryO%2F140e3ef2ef514b9fa271f86590c6521e%2F2904.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" alt="2904.png"><img src="https://www.azuki.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fj7912igus1qi%2F3jGkGS24z12WaHfuJ86fAg%2Fb171e4ebaf3820d7fc6f6a5211199c4b%2F5889.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" alt="5889.png"><p>Spirit of Satoshi PBT collectors were able to equip their Azukis with the Azuki x SATOSHI NAKAMOTO hoodie.</p><p>Spirit Emblem collectors were eligible to claim the Azuki x SATOSHI NAKAMOTO Special Edition Enduro Hoodie.</p><img src="https://www.azuki.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fj7912igus1qi%2F4tRzHWGXMD5301M6ae1f2T%2F1c026ea2f8edd47f1fb370f4f779ef1c%2F03-hoodie_image_1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" alt="03-hoodie image 1.jpg"><img src="https://www.azuki.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fj7912igus1qi%2F2Ey0MfmlfmTzcADljpuePv%2F30ec11aeb0a617fd1589aa80468df55e%2F03-hoodie_image_2.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" alt="03-hoodie image 2.jpg"><img src="https://www.azuki.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fj7912igus1qi%2F6KFFjwCHipWnzqAjKj0T9l%2Feae1206336aea10b0b59fed6902348c7%2F03-hoodie_image_3.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" alt="03-hoodie image 3.jpg">`,

    'short': `On October 31st 2008, Satoshi Nakamoto published the Bitcoin whitepaper, sparking a global revolution. On the same date 15 year later, we collaborated with the fashion brand SATOSHI NAKAMOTO to create the special edition Azuki x SATOSHI NAKAMOTO Enduro Hoodie with the first dual-chain Physical Backed Token (PBT) chip embedded in each.`,
